<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Samurai on Balance Guides</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/</link><description>Recent content in Samurai on Balance Guides</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 02:52:16 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Samurai Basic Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/basic-guide/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 02:52:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/basic-guide/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="foreword">Foreword&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>As of Dawntrail, Samurai has been part of the game for seven years. As part of the team, I am updating this guide for Dawntrail as we have gotten a substantial amount of changes upon release, until 7.05 which marked a big shift in gameplay since Shadowbringers, and will be covered in this document. This guide is intended for newer and older players alike.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>-Zheng&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>The following section summarizes Samurai’s abilities. You may also refer to &lt;a href="https://na.finalfantasyxiv.com/jobguide/samurai/">Square Enix’s Samurai Job Guide&lt;/a> for specific skill and trait text. Feel free to skip this section if you are familiar with Samurai’s skills.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Samurai Skills Overview</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/skills-overview/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 02:48:24 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/skills-overview/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="samurai-skills-overview">Samurai Skills Overview&lt;/h1>
